Overview

This phase is investigation-only. No code was modified.

Current tenancy model observed in runtime code:
- Frontend tenant context is path-based under /store/:slug via route guard + TenantService.
- Backend tenant context is header-based via X-Tenant-Slug in TenantResolutionMiddleware.
- Tenant identity is enforced by JWT tenantId claim matching resolved tenant context.

Migration target assessed in this inventory:
- Move from path-based tenant URL identity to host/domain-based tenant identity.


