  Exact behavior:
  - For authenticated requests, compares JWT tenant claim (tenantId/tenant_id/etc.) with resolved ITenantContext.TenantId.
  - Denies if mismatch or claim missing.
  Conceptual change for host/domain model:
  - Works with domain model if ITenantContext resolves from host.
